Description: This class contains the "startInterview" class button (Start Interview) that opens the interview page
This class contains the "restartBtn" class button (Home) that returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
This class contains the "btnStart" class button (Start) that starts the interview and the "btn" buttons that each represent an answer
This class contains the "btnShowTranscript" class button (Show Transcript) that shows the transcript of the interview when clicked
This class contains the transcript and the "btnRevisitQ" class button (Revisit this question)
This class contains the "btnConclusion" class button (Show Conclusion) that opens the conclusion page
This class contains the "btnDownloadTranscript" class button (Download Transcript) that download the transcript
This class contains the "backToWelcomePage" class button (Home) that returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
